name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Flip Through Floor Sanding and Polishin

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Ctrl+Shift+Right or Ctrl+Shift+Left to flip through window tabs while researching floor sanding and polishing

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This Extension provides a Flip Through tool when searching Brisbane Floor sanding and Polishing tabs. 

The tool was designed for Brisbane Timber Floors, a premium Brisbane floor sanding company in QLD Australia. 

After leading the market with UV cured technology, BTF has taken to digital solutions such as this Chrome Browser as the next step in their ambitious expansion plans.
